HEADWORD: Sychnocarpous
<hw>Sych`no*car"pous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ much
or frequent + <?/ fruit.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having the
